{"word":"G459 - ἄνομος - ánomos - an'-om-os - Without law","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄνομος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ánomos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an'-om-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Without law</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அக்கிரமமான, சட்டத்துக்குப் புறம்பான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. destitute of (the Mosaic) law"},{"paragraph":"2. departing from the law, a violator of the law, lawless, wicked"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G3551 - νόμος - nómos - nom'-os/3551\">G3551</a>; <i>lawless</i>, that is, (negatively) <i>not subject to</i> (the Jewish) <i>law</i>; (by implication a <i>Gentile</i>), or (positively) <i>wicked:</i> - without law, lawless, transgressor, unlawful, wicked.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1772/1772\">G1772</a>, <a href=\"#/G3544/3544\">G3544</a>, <a href=\"#/G3545/3545\">G3545</a>, <a href=\"#/G3547/3547\">G3547</a>, <a href=\"#/G3548/3548\">G3548</a>, <a href=\"#/G3549/3549\">G3549</a>, <a href=\"#/G3550/3550\">G3550</a>, <a href=\"#/G3551/3551\">G3551</a>, <a href=\"#/G3891/3891\">G3891</a>, <a href=\"#/G3892/3892\">G3892</a>, <a href=\"#/G458/458\">G458</a>, <a href=\"#/G459/459\">G459</a>, <a href=\"#/G460/460\">G460</a>"}]}